  "title": "IT Automation Tester",
  "description": "<p>Design test scenarios and translate into Advanced Jbehaves​</p><p>Review test scenarios with PO to ensure completeness and add meta tagging for future reusability​</p><p>Expert in JIRA, BDD and Zephyr management. Execute and upload test artefacts. Defect management to ensure timely retest, ensure closure with proper RCA​</p><p>Prepare test data requirement​</p><p>Support test management daily report, participate in daily stand-up and related ceremonies​</p><p>Track downtime, maintain regression pack​</p><p>Prepare training materials​</p><p>Support live implementation and post-implementation issues​</p><p>Experience in database and JAVA library management​</p><p>Knowledge and experience in automation framework such as Selenium, Appium or Playwright</p><p><br /></p><p>Internal ref: 10058</p><p><br /></p><p>Thanks, and Best Regards</p><p>Lini</p><p>Recruitment Consultant</p><p>R22108463</p>",
